  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON: Due to the lack of traditional design and materials the proposed replacement shopfront with a fully glazed design is inappropriate, causing unacceptable harm to the character and appearance of the host building and the wider conservation area. The proposal would therefore be contrary to the guidance contained within the Islington Shopfront Design Guide (2003) and the Chapel Market/Penton Street Conservation Area Design Gude.  The proposal would be further contrary to policy CS12 of the Core Strategy (2012) and policy DM 4.8 of the Development Management Policies (2013)."
